{"tid":689873,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【惺渣ga】恐怖分子威脅斬首 C 朗請鬥牛勇士做保鑣","createTime":"2018-06-04T11:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T07:06:38.000Z","uid":20634,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"11d521a980b091b2b8b208811c123964fa863321","tid":689873,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"早前極端組織伊斯蘭國 ( IS ) 曾表示，要在今屆俄羅斯世界盃進行期間發動恐怖襲擊，又聲言要將球壇兩大巨星 C 朗拿度和美斯斬首，正所謂寧可信其有，不可信其無， C 朗拿度特意請來私人保鑣貼身保護自己和家人。<br />\n<br />\n經過千挑萬選後， C 朗拿度最後請來身高 6 尺 2 寸的鬥牛勇士 Nuno Marecos 擔任私人保鑣， Nuno Marecos 除了懂得鬥牛外，亦曾做過傘兵，並參加過 MMA 比賽，可於陸空兩棲作戰，事實上， C 朗拿度對於 Nuno Marecos 一點也不陌生，因為今屆歐聯決賽，他亦聘用對方作為自己的私人保鑣。<br />\n<br />\n既然有 Nuno Marecos 這種猛人作貼身保護，相信 C 朗拿度可能專心備戰，為葡萄牙爭取好成績。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/UGTdVExfgjU/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FUGTdVExfgjU%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=30a3da07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HkMW4uKnVoA/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FHkMW4uKnVoA%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=4031f6ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"853a5ebd4083edc4e4df9fc87de7e8790d3c9f15","tid":689873,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:50:24.000Z","msg":"仲矮過我 me6尺6"},{"pid":"10ef50991cc0ef2b0c748da473116d3be60a52df","tid":689873,"uid":34419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T16:30:28.000Z","msg":"請返去同牙朗練拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d5093a4c5896e08dcffd4adcd97fcc58dcb066","tid":689873,"uid":19126,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T17:12:08.000Z","msg":"原來牙朗係決賽俾保鏢保護到消失左<br />\n<br />\n唔好怪佢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e178e4aeaac3071fe